      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "Concept ACK\r\n\r\nThe additional cost of bumping the parent should be taken into account when calculating the effective value of the unconfirmed UTXO. This would additionally dissuade selection of UTXOs with low fee rate parent transactions, especially when we start preferring coin selection results with a lower waste as proposed in https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/22009.\r\n\r\nI am goint to take a stab at implementing the auto-fee leveling.",
